BIDS-apps Nextflow Pipeline
============================


Runs any BIDS application on a BIDS dataset.


USAGE:
	nextflow bids.nf -c <NF_CONF> [options] --bids <BIDS_DIR> --out <OUT_DIR>

ARGUMENTS:
	-c	 					Nextflow configuration file of BIDS application
	--bids 						BIDS dataset directory (full path)
	--out						BIDS derivatives directory to output into


OPTIONAL ARGUMENTS: (default values pre-specified by config)

	--simg <simg>				Which singularity container to use
	--invocation <invocation_json>		Boutiques invocation JSON containing BIDS-app args
	--descriptor <descriptor_json>		Boutiques descriptor JSON containing commandline
						specification
	--rewrite				Overwrite existing subjects
	--subjects <subject_txt>		Subjects list

SUPPORTED PROFILES

	-profile (kimel|scc|local)		On which system to run the cifti_clean pipeline

NOTES:
By default all existing subjects WILL NOT be overwritten, instead they will be skipped.
All logging information will be stored in <OUT_DIR>/pipeline_logs/${application_name}/<subject_name>.(err|out).
